QuestData.Title: The Last Stand
QuestData.Description: $n, I desperately need your help! I cannot hold out forever against this demonic onslaught. If I fall, Astranaar is next!$B$BPlease help me!
QuestData.RewardText: You've saved us all, $n! I have the power to finish off these final few.$B$BNo longer will the forest have to fear the Burning Legion!
